OL,6,FA controlling husband who stabbed his
OL,7,Fwife to death as she pushed their baby
OL,8,Fin a pram after tracking her to a
OL,9,Fwomen's refuge is to be sentenced on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FHabibur Masum, 27, was found guilty of
OL,13,Fmurdering Kulsuma Akter in a
OL,14,F"ferocious" knife attack in broad
OL,15,Fdaylight before leaving her bleeding
OL,16,Fto death and calmly walking away,
OL,17,Fleaving their seven-month-old son
OL,18,Fbehind.
