OL,6,FMr Justice Cotter will set the minimum
OL,7,Fjail term for Masum's life sentence
OL,8,Fduring a hearing at Bradford Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FJurors at his trial heard Masum
OL,12,Ffollowed Ms Akter to a refuge in
OL,13,FBradford where she had been staying to
OL,14,Fescape him after he held a knife to
OL,15,Fher throat at their home in Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
