OL,3,CHusband who stabbed wife to death as
OL,4,Cshe pushed baby in pram to be sentenced
OL,6,FAfter finding her through her phone
OL,7,Flocation, Masum loitered in streets
OL,8,Faround the hostel and sent her
OL,9,Fmessages threatening to kill her
OL,10,Ffamily members if she did not return
OL,11,Fto him, before trying to lure her out
OL,12,Fby sending her fake messages from a
OL,13,Flocal GP practice pretending their son
OL,14,Fhad an appointment.
OL,16,FThe court heard Ms Akter eventually
OL,17,Ffelt safe enough to leave the refuge
OL,18,Fon April 6 last year after Masum
OL,19,Fupdated his Facebook page falsely
OL,20,Fclaiming to be in Spain.
