OL,3,CHusband who stabbed wife to death as
OL,4,Cshe pushed baby in pram to be sentenced
OL,6,FAs she was walking in the city centre
OL,7,Fwith a friend, pushing her baby in a
OL,8,Fpram, Masum confronted her, the trial
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FCCTV footage of the attack captured Ms
OL,12,FAkter's screams as Masum stabbed her
OL,13,Fat least 25 times.
OL,15,FJurors heard he then calmly walked
OL,16,Fthrough Bradford city centre and was
OL,17,Fseen on CCTV grinning as he got on a
OL,18,Fbus, believing at that point he was
OL,19,Fgetting away.
