OL,3,CHusband who stabbed wife to death as
OL,4,Cshe pushed baby in pram to be sentenced
OL,6,FMasum travelled almost 200 miles south
OL,7,Fto Aylesbury, Buckinghamshire, and was
OL,8,Farrested in the early hours of April 9
OL,9,Fin a car park near Stoke Mandeville
OL,10,FHospital, where he had gone to be
OL,11,Ftreated for "lockjaw".
OL,13,FThe trial heard the relationship
OL,14,Fbetween Masum and Ms Akter was "an
OL,15,Fabusive relationship characterised by
OL,16,Fhis jealousy, possessiveness and
OL,17,Fcontrolling behaviour".
