OL,3,CHusband who stabbed wife to death as
OL,4,Cshe pushed baby in pram to be sentenced
OL,6,FThe couple met and married in
OL,7,FBangladesh, and came to the UK in 2022
OL,8,Fafter he obtained a student visa and
OL,9,Fenrolled on a Masters course to study
OL,10,Fmarketing.
OL,12,FThey moved into a house in Oldham
OL,13,Ftogether in September 2022.
OL,15,FOn November 23 2023, he became jealous
OL,16,Fover a "completely innocuous" message
OL,17,FMs Akter received from a male
OL,18,Fcolleague and held a knife to her
OL,19,Fthroat.
